Thomas B. Cusick 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President of Finance, CFO and Treasurer at COLUMBIA SPORTSWEAR CO, Thomas B. Cusick  made $1,411,580 in total compensation.  Of this total $572,970 was received as a salary, $348,332 was received as a bonus, $193,505 was received in stock options, $236,514 was awarded as stock and $60,259 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


