Thomas B. Cusick



Mr. Thomas B. Cusick, CPA, is Chief Operating Officer & Executive Vice President at Columbia Sportswear Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Barrett Business Services, Inc. Mr. Cusick was previously employed as Accountant by KPMG LLP.



