Columbia Sportswear Co. »
Columbia Sportswear Company is a leading innovator in the global outdoor apparel, footwear, accessories and equipment markets. We design, develop, market and distribute active outdoor products under the following brands:
Columbia Sportswear

Founded in 1938, Columbia Sportswear apparel, footwear accessories and equipment have earned a reputation for innovation, quality and performance, serving the needs of outdoor enthusiasts in more than 100 countries.




